    public class IntTreeBag
extends java.lang.Object

    This class is a homework assignment; An IntTreeBag is a collection of int numbers. Limitations: Beyond Integer.MAX_VALUE elements, countOccurrences, and size are wrong. Outline of Java Source Code for this class: http://www.cs.colorado.edu/~main/edu/colorado/collections/IntTreeBag.java Note: This file contains only blank implementations ("stubs") because this is a Programming Project for my students.
